title: Neil Young - Dreamin' Man Live '92 [320k MP3]
description:
Dreamin' Man Live '92 is a live album by Neil Young, released on December 8, 2009. It features live, solo acoustic performances of all ten songs from Harvest Moon, recorded on tour in 1992. The album is volume twelve in Young's Archives Performance Series and the fifth to be released.[5] It was originally slated for release on November 2, 2009, but was delayed for over a month; a vinyl release followed on March 30, 2010.
